The Lagos State Police Command has arrested Lagos-based businessman, Amara Kennedy, who was accused of circulating nude photos of single mothers he had a relationship with. The development was reportedly confirmed on Friday by one of the victims, Kester. Kennedy who was spreading nude photos of single mothers and widows she had relationships with in church WhatsApp groups and various other platforms, had been on the run. Meanwhile, the family of the suspect has condemned his actions and publicly disowned him for bringing disgrace to their family.